<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$su-su-44" href="/people/su-su-44">苏簌</a>，<strong title="如果你把所有的错误都关在门外，那么真理也要被关在门外了呢。" class="zu-question-my-bio">如果你把所有的错误都关在门外，那么真理…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="15">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yang-lei-24-6" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yang-lei-24-6" class="zg-link" title="杨磊">杨磊</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhi-shi-que-fa-kong-ju-zheng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhi-shi-que-fa-kong-ju-zheng" class="zg-link" title="知识缺乏恐惧症">知识缺乏恐惧症</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lu-sheng-xing-96" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lu-sheng-xing-96" class="zg-link" title="妖风">妖风</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="410721" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">现在的姑娘眼光都很奇葩，没有统一喜好，唯一准则是你观察她自己的着装，搭配她的英伦风嘻哈风日系森系或OL等，那就不会错的了。<br>有的放矢啊我的朋友。


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
